parameters: "Ah, it's a snapping turtle! A snapping turtle! Wow, it's so creepy!"
"Do you like Ao too? Rare things are nice, aren't they?"
(I think Hinori is quite a rare girl too..)

"The water is surprisingly clear.. Oh, mud splashes every time I take a
step.."
"Be careful not to step on the crops, okay?"
"Oh, it's a tadpole.. It'll be lively when autumn comes, won't it?"
"There seem to be a lot of larvae.. but I'm not going to search for them."
"You know, it'll be really beautiful when autumn comes."
The bridge is broken and cannot be crossed.
